# Running tests

When running unit tests or the full test suite, use the same command as the project owner:

```bash
cd /home/sysop/projects/python/dbconform && uv run dbconform test run 2>&1
```

Do not use `uv run pytest tests/unit/` or raw `pytest` for test runs; use **`uv run dbconform test run`** so the test CLI handles the environment and output consistently.
